{"tid":2208911,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"未曾離別已不捨 - 陳惜姿","createTime":"2020-09-19T09:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T09:20:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0be08556518ede766a96ab85fe9c3daecb276190","tid":2208911,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09:16:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200919/RLSUS7WUIJEOHIJ4YOR74JX574/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200919%2FRLSUS7WUIJEOHIJ4YOR74JX574%2F&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=36a7f68a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200919%2FRLSUS7WUIJEOHIJ4YOR74JX574%2F&h=7c04ef43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200919/RLSUS7WUIJEOHIJ4YOR74JX574/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n未曾離別已不捨 - 陳惜姿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Vz24dn7CwO_XSMv_K2PYF5rO7jc=/5076x3102/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WH24FIFSGRAJDHKEP2AYEOH5NI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVz24dn7CwO_XSMv_K2PYF5rO7jc%3D%2F5076x3102%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWH24FIFSGRAJDHKEP2AYEOH5NI.jpg&h=8a3513e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大學同學談移民，已非新鮮話題。有人連BNO都等不及，分享別人帶着一家大小在倫敦機場用LOTR闖關的經歷，我只問，要走得那麼急嗎？<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。突然想，自己若要離開，將來思鄉，會緬懷香港的什麼。<br />\n<br />\n有些事本與我無關，車駛至文華酒店，我想起張國榮的死。瞥見酒店外的黃銅欄杆，想到那恐怖一天的新聞片段，天昏地暗。酒店外的行車隧道，2014年佔中時空蕩蕩，隧道兩旁寫滿字，行人漫步拍照，詭異非常。如今隧道內汽車呼嘯而過，兩旁又鋪滿厚黑灰塵。<br />\n<br />\n經過干諾道天橋，想起西環曾經有一家以鬼作主題的餐廳，侍應都以猛鬼打扮，食客也給化粧師弄得鬼五馬六。現在餐廳應沒有了，但想起許多年前，那個跟好友吚嘩鬼叫慶生的晚上，仍是莞爾。轉入西邊街更是熟悉了，那是我上大學的地方，那斜路爬過不知多少次，有天無聊，明明不是天主教徒，走進港大對面的天主堂看看彌撒是怎樣子。<br />\n<br />\n那只是一小段路，別說偌大一個香港。記憶是個人的，這些足跡編織成今天的我。未曾離別已不捨，想到離開心會痛，便是我好鍾意香港的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n==============<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8028b7a0969a1333a14edcc915630539390d628","tid":2208911,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}